  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AssociationConstrainable
    A tagging interface that tags an ObjectToObject link to indicate that it is allowed to have AssociationConstraints.
    AssociationConstraintItem
    This interface represents one item of an AssociationConstraint.
    AssociationConstraintService
    Manages AssociationConstraint and AssociationConstraintItem objects and validations.
